title: Venezuelan post-rock outfit Zeta perform Live on KEXP. Out now on our channel 📺
Zeta - Full Performance (Live on KEXP)
description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents Zeta performing live in the KEXP studio. Recorded March 31, 2023

Songs:
La Flor De La Palabra
Completar
La Flor Del Tiempo
Magia Infinita

Juan Ricardo Yilo Alvarado - Vocals, guitar, congas
Daniel Eduardo Saud - Vocals, guitar, organ, percussion
Antonio Pereira - Bass
Josue Vargas - Keys, synth
Carlos De Lima - Minor Percussion
Eduardo Sandoval - Drums

Host: Albina Cabrera
Audio Engineers: Jon Roberts
Audio Mixer: Jon Roberts
Mastering: Matt Ogaz
Cameras: Jim Beckmann, Carlos Cruz, Scott Holpainen, Luke Knecht
Editor: Scott Holpainen
